Lets transform it into a list of labels and a list of sentences:

```elixir
{labels, utterances} =
  "disco.json"
  |> File.read!()
  |> Jason.decode!()
  |> Enum.flat_map(fn %{"id" => id, "training_data" => training_data} ->
    training_data |> Enum.map(&{id, &1})
  end)
  |> Enum.unzip()
```

