First of all, the labels. We want to encode these as numbers instead of text labels, and make them into a tensor.

```elixir
lookup = labels |> Enum.uniq() |> Enum.with_index() |> Map.new()
labels_tensor = labels |> Enum.map(&lookup[&1]) |> Nx.tensor()
```

